{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idab8a1583-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s10109"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"10109"},"text":"§ 10109.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Marine Corps Reserve: administration","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idab8a1584-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s10109/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The Marine Corps Reserve is the reserve component of the Marine Corps. It shall be organized, administered, trained, and supplied under the direction of the Commandant of the Marine Corps.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idab8a1585-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s10109/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The departments and offices of Headquarters, Marine Corps have the same relation and responsibilities to the Marine Corps Reserve as they do to the Regular Marine Corps.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idab8a1586-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"(Added ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/337/dA/tXVI/s1661/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–337, div. A, title XVI, § 1661(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-10-05"},"text":"Oct. 5, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/2971"},"text":"108 Stat. 2971","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idab8a1587-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idab8a1588-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"hea